208
00:23:05,807 --> 00:23:07,707
Is this only allowed for the Apostles?

209
00:23:07,707 --> 00:23:13,106
Then is it also only allowed for them to baptize, give the Holy Spirit, and cleanse the sins of the nations?

210
00:23:13,106 --> 00:23:16,406
Because all of this was commanded to no one else but the Apostles.

211
00:23:16,406 --> 00:23:26,854
But if in one place, both the loosening of bonds and the power of the sacrament are given; either all of it is derived to us from the form and power of the Apostles, or none of it is released from the decrees.

212
00:23:26,854 --> 00:24:55,240
"I, Paul, laid the foundation, and another builds on it,"
First Corinthians 3:10.
