216
00:25:15,540 --> 00:25:25,261
With great weight and balance, after many groans, shedding of tears, and the prayers of the whole church, true repentance is not denied pardon, so that no one prejudges Christ, who will judge.

217
00:25:25,261 --> 00:25:29,565
If you write more clearly what you think, brother, you will be more fully instructed.

218
00:25:29,565 --> 00:25:39,336
