226
00:26:10,829 --> 00:26:21,866
And what I have forgiven—if there was anything to forgive—I have forgiven in the sight of Christ for your sake, in order that Satan might not outwit us; for we are not unaware of his schemes Second Corinthians 2:10-11.

227
00:26:21,866 --> 00:26:27,182
