267
00:30:16,049 --> 00:30:17,326
What if you had denied it?

268
00:30:17,326 --> 00:30:18,701
Nature would have cried out.

269
00:30:18,701 --> 00:30:20,960
Or if you still have doubts, let’s keep quiet.

270
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:25,036
Both of us will be whatever we are called, with the age of the name as our witness.

271
00:30:25,036 --> 00:30:30,535
