963
01:40:20,397 --> 01:40:24,474
Not to the image of the Christian community, nor to the form of the faithful.

964
01:40:24,474 --> 01:40:28,181
I am glad to be taught; but I am displeased that it is not understood.

965
01:40:28,181 --> 01:40:29,240
