1134
02:07:10,983 --> 02:07:16,298
(Psalm 119:7)
And not to ignore Solomon’s saying: A brother helping a brother will be exalted.

1135
02:07:16,298 --> 02:07:18,673
(Proverbs 18:9)
What does the Apostle say?

1136
02:07:18,673 --> 02:07:27,099
Brothers, if someone is caught in a sin, you who are spiritual should restore that person gently, watching yourselves so you also may not be tempted.

1137
02:07:27,099 --> 02:07:31,567
Carry each other’s burdens, and in this way you will fulfill the law of Christ.

1138
