02:08:14,657 --> 02:08:16,806
Is there no speck in your eyes, I ask?

1145
02:08:16,806 --> 02:08:20,595
Who will boast of having a pure heart, or of being clean from sins?

1146
02:08:20,595 --> 02:08:23,083
(Proverbs 20:9, according to the Septuagint)

1147
02:08:24,383 --> 02:08:34,399
